11¿Õ»ó 7:13 Now King Solomon sent and brought Hiram from Tyre.
11¿Õ»ó 7:14 He was a widow's son from the tribe of Naphtali, and his father was a man of Tyre, a worker in bronze; and he was filled with wisdom and understanding and skill for doing any work in bronze. So he came to King Solomon and performed all his work.
