11¿Õ»ó 8:30 "And listen to the supplication of Thy servant and of Thy people Israel, when they pray toward this place; hear Thou in heaven Thy dwelling place; hear and forgive.
11¿Õ»ó 8:31 "If a man sins against his neighbor and is made to take an oath, and he comes [and] takes an oath before Thine altar in this house,
