11¿Õ»ó 21:29 "Do you see how Ahab has humbled himself before Me? Because he has humbled himself before Me, I will not bring the evil in his days, [but] I will bring the evil upon his house in his son's days."
11¿Õ»ó 22:1 And three years passed without war between Aram and Israel.
11¿Õ»ó 22:2 And it came about in the third year, that Jehoshaphat the king of Judah came down to the king of Israel.
