11¿Õ»ó 22:52 And he did evil in the sight of the LORD and walked in the way of his father and in the way of his mother and in the way of Jeroboam the son of Nebat, who caused Israel to sin.
11¿Õ»ó 22:53 So he served Baal and worshiped him and provoked the LORD God of Israel to anger according to all that his father had done.
